  "details": "This package provides all utilities for use in Bluetooth applications. The BLUETOOTH trademarks are owned by Bluetooth SIG, Inc., U.S.A.\r\n\r\nSecurity Fix(es):\r\n\r\nbluetoothd from bluez incorrectly saves adapters&apos; Discoverable status when a device is powered down, and restores it when powered up. If a device is powered down while discoverable, it will be discoverable when powered on again. This could lead to inadvertent exposure of the bluetooth stack to physically nearby attackers.(CVE-2021-3658)",
